{"h255bc9bcgfed7g41ebgb675ga888a3bc9772": ["*Chirp!*", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "1235862f-7462-3164-7949-7109331069aa"], "h94faf687g8f32g45cfg9b59gc348ce2e3903": ["Not now. Places to be.", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "5f765554-b242-aa36-0523-4bddcedce20c"], "h78392a96ge3acg49e1ga255g5d108c1166b8": ["Where are you going?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "073ded13-cd2b-24ca-acd9-75b0c24ee5e5"], "h9c91b21fge5a5g45e6g96acg1ecd2b90b28f": ["To find Halsin. There's not a moment to lose!", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "fc1a3c91-203a-3177-2cfb-d9f496cc9880"], "h07d8fdd8ga3cfg4993g849bgd8d20bf3e870": ["What's the rush?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "1edefcc4-807e-da42-6559-56b8ec3292ea"], "he7eb0423g56c7g4d99gb7a1g727a715f3564": ["I have to find Halsin. There's not a moment to lose!", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "af2c82b5-249c-2e88-d228-659c01352871"], "h6a331bbdg9e60g4d88gad3fg01be8493d9c6": ["I need information, friend. Spare me a moment?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "2bf8753e-1525-5e24-2317-f2e98b426822"], "h09997ca2g3eedg45f4g90a5gcd25d3e8e124": ["For one of our own. But be quick.", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "dcea68e3-9bd2-07d9-d79e-8997c4899a55"], "h3c00603agfe6eg415fg85b3g1d736cc2dae8": ["What's waiting for us outside this grove? In the wilds?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "7d54ebe9-db2a-4536-bbb4-9d4c57bf9638"], "hc78af089gf901g4f4fgb4e6ga6893da76e87": ["Goblins. Gnolls. All manner of monsters!", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "38bac0e7-fb31-780c-de83-70a234267706"], "hb2a12d91gb2cag4614gb836g768e620c6f56": ["Goblins. Gnolls. Even elves that look like you.", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "38bac0e7-fb31-780c-de83-70a234267706"], "hb922667cg88c5g441bgaa8cg9ac6b06e8bf2": ["Goblins. Gnolls. Even a couple of your underground cousins. ", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "38bac0e7-fb31-780c-de83-70a234267706"], "hce88ccb1g0e93g4c44g91e6g82d50dfdf2ed": ["Now I have to go. There's not a moment to lose! ", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "63c70028-672a-341e-34bc-221e5916b753"], "h020c305egff3bg4c12g999cg626031c6bb68": ["*He flutters into the air without another word, setting off at a determined pace.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "c32bd213-37ac-53f7-396a-7e6c237fecaa"], "h16888ef5g620fg4e5ag8c45g94c0fac439ce": ["Do you know Baldur's Gate? Is the city far?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "529a8474-d9a2-b9af-8f5b-a984e96e322f"], "h0a1c064cga961g4f5agab20g1ab49b9d7916": ["I know these hills, and there's no city here.", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "96b2acfd-3cf4-3e35-bced-7103a312c831"], "h82d303bcg9c95g47c7g8a9dgd17845a1ced0": ["I'm looking for the druid Halsin. Where is he? ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "60367e26-3a45-40fd-cc8d-893e7323b29b"], "hf5ef66a3g0aedg488eg981agdc0fc4a46be0": ["That's what I'm trying to find out! ", "bf90aa40-232b-40fd-a43e-699bb964e337", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "b500a419-0cbf-5ed3-3ae3-1b8719cfcc1a"], "h871b9593gda91g4d7dg95a5g671c148e629d": ["Never mind. Off you go.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "90e9b549-9b2e-c0c3-4e88-62e15e7836b1"], "haba7c503g2e7dg441agaa36g96d0f2194bd8": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_Apprentice_Bird.html", "678173aa-2844-63fd-14de-2e3845a1d6cb"]}